=head1 NAME

AIRT - Application for Incident Response Teams


=head1 DESCRIPTION

Computer security incident response teams need to track incidents as they
develop. AIRT is a web-based system to provide incident tracking
capabilities to computer security incident response teams.

AIRT is a PHP web application with some command-line components, built on
top of a relational database. Information on how to set up the initial
database for AIRT can be found in F<@AIRT_DOCDIR@/README>.


